  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/579720/extras/8fcdc5460ba6573d5197acdd2c3ff84a.poster.avif?t=1728555958\" width=616 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/579720/extras/8fcdc5460ba6573d5197acdd2c3ff84a.webm?t=1728555958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/579720/extras/8fcdc5460ba6573d5197acdd2c3ff84a.mp4?t=1728555958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔹🔷 FEATURES  🔷🔹</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎲 Over <strong>60 </strong>challenging levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎲 4 unique zones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎲 <strong>Dualplay </strong>- play with or without VR headset.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎲 Compact, <strong>comfortable </strong>Play Area.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎲 Truly brain-teasing puzzles and riddles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎲 Cube-based labyrinth with traps, quantum physics and out of box solutions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/579720/extras/86aca49b37985b7d2efb91a265877afc.poster.avif?t=1728555958\" width=616 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/579720/extras/86aca49b37985b7d2efb91a265877afc.webm?t=1728555958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/579720/extras/86aca49b37985b7d2efb91a265877afc.mp4?t=1728555958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔹🔷 SUMMARY 🔷🔹</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎲 <strong>Neverout </strong>is a game like no other. It takes huge inspiration from the most classic '<strong>Escape Room</strong>' in history. The game features <strong>reality bending</strong>, <strong>quantum </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>physics</strong>, traps, obstacles and puzzles. All soaked in <strong>otherworldly </strong>and surreal setting. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎲 The players will test their imagination, sense of logic, '<strong>out-of-the-bo</strong>x' thinking and how quick and swift they can adapt to <strong>ever-changing</strong> reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎲 'Up' can become 'down', 'floor' - 'ceiling'. Fire might freeze and ice start burning. But there's <strong>always</strong> logic behind the madness and one thing is certain - there is <strong>always </strong>a solution.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But some...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come with <strong>sacrifices</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/579720/extras/b41f9f80fdb66153d85dd186b0bfe47a.poster.avif?t=1728555958\" width=616 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/579720/extras/b41f9f80fdb66153d85dd186b0bfe47a.webm?t=1728555958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/579720/extras/b41f9f80fdb66153d85dd186b0bfe47a.mp4?t=1728555958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/579720/extras/8fcdc5460ba6573d5197acdd2c3ff84a.poster.avif?t=1728555958\" width=616 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/579720/extras/8fcdc5460ba6573d5197acdd2c3ff84a.webm?t=1728555958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/579720/extras/8fcdc5460ba6573d5197acdd2c3ff84a.mp4?t=1728555958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔹🔷 FEATURES  🔷🔹</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎲 Over <strong>60 </strong>challenging levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎲 4 unique zones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎲 <strong>Dualplay </strong>- play with or without VR headset.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎲 Compact, <strong>comfortable </strong>Play Area.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎲 Truly brain-teasing puzzles and riddles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎲 Cube-based labyrinth with traps, quantum physics and out of box solutions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/579720/extras/86aca49b37985b7d2efb91a265877afc.poster.avif?t=1728555958\" width=616 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/579720/extras/86aca49b37985b7d2efb91a265877afc.webm?t=1728555958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/579720/extras/86aca49b37985b7d2efb91a265877afc.mp4?t=1728555958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔹🔷 SUMMARY 🔷🔹</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎲 <strong>Neverout </strong>is a game like no other. It takes huge inspiration from the most classic '<strong>Escape Room</strong>' in history. The game features <strong>reality bending</strong>, <strong>quantum </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>physics</strong>, traps, obstacles and puzzles. All soaked in <strong>otherworldly </strong>and surreal setting. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎲 The players will test their imagination, sense of logic, '<strong>out-of-the-bo</strong>x' thinking and how quick and swift they can adapt to <strong>ever-changing</strong> reality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎲 'Up' can become 'down', 'floor' - 'ceiling'. Fire might freeze and ice start burning. But there's <strong>always</strong> logic behind the madness and one thing is certain - there is <strong>always </strong>a solution.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But some...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come with <strong>sacrifices</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/579720/extras/b41f9f80fdb66153d85dd186b0bfe47a.poster.avif?t=1728555958\" width=616 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/579720/extras/b41f9f80fdb66153d85dd186b0bfe47a.webm?t=1728555958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/579720/extras/b41f9f80fdb66153d85dd186b0bfe47a.mp4?t=1728555958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
